🎯 Key Concepts Explained
JWT Token: Stateless auth token. Includes user ID, expires in 3 days
Bcrypt: Hashes password with 10 salt rounds. Plain text never stored
Mongoose Schema: Validates data before saving to MongoDB
Middleware: express.json() parses incoming JSON requests
Pre-save Hook: Automatically hashes password before MongoDB insert
Nodemailer: Sends emails via Gmail SMTP
